{"tid":1789262,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"領展37億元購澳洲悉尼商廈　首次衝出亞洲","createTime":"2019-12-19T09:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:29:49.000Z","uid":10199,"like":30,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"12d5da45faa91a661cc2105a91080b16968d52a1","tid":1789262,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"領展\t（00823） 衝出亞洲，宣布以約6.83億澳元（約36.7億港元）向私募基金黑石（Blackstone）購入一幢位於澳洲悉尼100 Market Street、樓高十層的甲級商業樓宇。集團稱，未來會繼續開拓海外其他已發展市場，除澳洲，也會考慮新加坡、日本及英國等門戶城市。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁王國龍表示，收購海外物業將令資產組合更多元化，為公司開拓新收入來源，有助減低香港物業作為收入增長來源的依賴，讓公司循更健康的軌道擴張。<br />\n<br />\n繼續以香港為基地及主要市場<br />\n<br />\n領展強調，集團會繼續以香港為基地及主要市場，但海外已發展市場的發展成熟並較穩定，且具有一定的流動性和透明的監管制度，均屬投資考慮之列。"},{"pid":"af30d4ecfbb4a27acc885502a9eb2fc3d0234581","tid":1789262,"uid":82881,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"點解樹仔收購唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4899a9de2057f955e5a33c49806d73a128876e","tid":1789262,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"聽日升上100蚊？"},{"pid":"0caba0cbfa6b93c45f5f9e3a7e6b4668cbe738f0","tid":1789262,"uid":62424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"af30d4ecfbb4a27acc885502a9eb2fc3d0234581","tid":1789262,"uid":82881,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"點解樹仔收購唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"收購既野都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfeb6c54a50087ad9a8a0baeb6dfd17425cf83a","tid":1789262,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"走了走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4